
<!DOCTYPE>
<html>
<head>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=640, initial-scale=0.5, user-scalable=0.5, minimum-scale=0.5, maximum-scale=1" />

<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black" />
<meta name="apple-itunes-app" content="app-id=577710538,app-argument=dface://login/" />
<meta http-equiv="mobile-agent" content="format=xhtml; url=http://dface.cn/mini.html" />
<title>紫薇原点祈福活动</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="w/1/css/public.css" type="text/css" media="screen"/>
<script src="w/1/js/jquery-1.6.2.min.js" language="javascript" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script>

</script>
</head>

<body>
<div class="main">
  <div class="header2"><img src="w/1/images/header2.png"/></div>
  <div class="con">
    <div class="plane2">
      <div class="imgsbox">
        <!-- <img class="imgs" src="w/1/images/pic1.jpg"> -->
        <%= image_tag "http://dface.cn/zw#{params[:id]}.jpg" , :class => "imgs" %>
        <img class="imgs2" src="w/1/images/pic3.png">
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <div class="tit">
          <%= image_tag @zwyd_wish.user_logo, :align => "absbottom" %>
          <h2><a href="#"><%= @zwyd_wish.photo_user.try(:name) %></a>的心愿：</h2>
        </div>
        <p><%= @zwyd_wish.photo_desc %></p>
        <div class="op">
          <b class="l">收到<%= @zwyd_wish.total %>个祝福</b>
          <a class="r" href="#">祝福他</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="plane3">
      <pre>我已经收到 <span class="red"><%= @zwyd_wish.total %></span>个祝福啦<br/><span class="red">还差<%= (99- @zwyd_wish.total.to_i) < 0 ? 0: (99- @zwyd_wish.total.to_i)   %>个祝福就能拿到新年红包啦，赶紧祝福我噢~</span></pre>
    </div>
    <div class="plane4">
      <ul>
        <% @zwyd_wish.data.reverse[0,3].each do |da| %>
         <li>
          <a href="#"><%= da.join(': ') %></a>
         </li>
        <% end %> 
      </ul>
      <div class="clear1"></div>
      <a class="r mr30" id="More" href="#">查看更多</a>
    </div>
    <div class="plane5">
      <div class="title1">祝福TA：</div>
      <form method="post" action="zwyd_wish/create">
        <%= hidden_field_tag :id, params[:id] %>
        <div class="inputbox1">
          <%= text_field_tag :name, params[:name]||'祝福人', :class => "texts" %>
        </div>
        <div class="inputbox2">
            <%= text_area_tag :wish, params[:wish]|| '祝福语'%>
        </div>
        <div class="clear1"></div>
        <input type="submit" class="btn r" value=" "/>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a href="http://www.dface.cn/mini.html" target="_blank"><img src="w/1/images/ad1.jpg" width="100%" class="mt10 mb30"/></a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
